Toss: Australia have won the toss and they will bat first. Australia are unchanged. Abdur Rehman replaces the injured Afridi and Junaid Khan replaces Aizaz Cheema.

The Pakistan seamers couldn't provide any breakthroughs in the first game, unlike the Australians. Junaid is a better wicket-taker than Cheema so it might be a good decision. Pakistan will be chasing tonight so it's important their bowlers keep Australia to a similar total on Tuesday. If Pakistan lose this, they lose the series as well.
